bib.title: Fast parameter-free multi-view subspace clustering with consensus anchor guidance
author: S Wang
X Liu
X Zhu
P Zhang
Y Zhang
bib.abstract: Multi-view subspace clustering has attracted intensive attention to effectively fuse multi-view information by exploring appropriate graph structures. Although existing works have made impressive progress in clustering performance, most of them suffer from the cubic time complexity which could prevent them from being efficiently applied into large-scale applications.
